text: Dušan Popeskov (born 5 June 1969) is a Serbian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics as an Independent Olympic Participant. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian male cyclists Category:Yugoslav male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists as Independent Olympic Participants Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
